Class Summary
CATest General purpose ClassAd tesing program.
Convert Program to demonstrate how to convert classads from one format to another.
ExprTest Main program to test evaluation of expressions.
Fetch Main program to fetch classads from the Condor collector and save them to a file.

PrintTest Simple test program to test parsing and printing classads.
QueryTest Main program to exercise the matching feature of classads.
 

Package condor.classad.tests Description

A package of tests for the classad package. This package includes tests to exercise the classad package both in isolation and in the context of Condor.
